@startuml
skinparam style strictuml
skinparam maxMessageSize 190

actor "Admin" as Admin
participant "AdminFeaturePanels.revenueStatsPanel\n(View)" as View
participant "AdminController\n(Facade)" as Facade
participant "RevenueStatsController" as Controller
participant "AdminService" as Service
participant "AdminRevenueRepository" as Repository
participant "JpaAdminDataStore" as DataStore
database "MySQL\n(BoardingHouse_DB)" as DB

Note over Admin, DB: QUY TRINH TONG HOP DOANH THU

Admin -> View : 1. Chon ky thong ke (MONTH/QUARTER/YEAR), nam, gia tri ky
View -> Facade : 2. refreshRevenue(period, year, periodValue)
activate Facade

Facade -> Controller : 3. refreshRevenue(period, year, periodValue)
activate Controller
Controller -> Service : 4. refreshRevenue(period, year, periodValue)
activate Service
Service -> Repository : 5. refreshRevenue(period, year, periodValue)
activate Repository
Repository -> DataStore : 6. refreshRevenue(period, year, periodValue)
activate DataStore

DataStore -> DB : 7. Truy van tong doanh thu HOA_DON da thu
activate DB
DB -->> DataStore : 8. invoice totals
DataStore -> DB : 9. Truy van tong BOI_THUONG da thu
DB -->> DataStore : 10. compensation totals
DataStore -->> Repository : 11. revenueRows da tong hop
Repository -->> Service : 12. revenueRows da tong hop
Service -->> Controller : 13. revenueRows da tong hop
Controller -->> Facade : 14. Da cap nhat du lieu
Facade -->> View : 15. Render chart/table + tong doanh thu

deactivate DB
deactivate DataStore
deactivate Repository
deactivate Service
deactivate Controller
deactivate Facade
@enduml
